            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ehelihuiz hueli mochihua campa neci tlahuazantli quence ayatl huan eltiuh achiyoc yayahuic quemman mopahpa miac tlahuazantli ica cehcanoc itlachiyaltiliz.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
